3 popular choice
1. Spring integration framework - A framework, recommended if you already have spring based application
2. Mule - A licensed software.
3. Apache camel - A framework, more adapters than Spring integration.

---------------

1.A2A, P2P
2.Spoke and Hub - Comes with default adapters to manage different standard communication format like txt/csv file formats, different databases, xml, API(SOAP/REST) etc.
				May need adapter for a proprietary application say SAP application. 
		
